lead_paragraph: Jeff Green scored 21 points, Marc Gasol added 15 points and eight rebounds, and the Memphis Grizzlies pulled away in the second half for a 103-83 victory over the Milwaukee Bucks on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Green Has 21 Points, Gasol 15 as Grizzlies Rout Bucks 103-83
